        "text": "## Iron(II) vs Iron(III): Ligand Coverage and Stability Comparison\n\n### Key Finding: 94 Distinct Ligands Studied with Both Fe²⁺ and Fe³⁺\n\nThe SRD-46 database contains data for **94 distinct ligands** that have been studied with both Fe²⁺ (metal_62, 217 total ligands) and Fe³⁺ (metal_61, 406 total ligands).",
